## Timeline HPAI outbreaks

## 24 Jan Kesteren

NL-HPAI(P)-2026-00004

Laying hen farm with around 45.000 hens distributed across 2 stables. In one stable in increase in the number of dead animals was suddenly 40. There are no other poultry farms within a 1 km radius bud 8 in a 3 km radius and 37 in the 10 km radius

## 26 Jan Alphen a.d. Rijn

NL-HPAI(NON-P)-2026-00019

Petting farm with pigs and several different birds including rare breeds. Pigs have been tested and were negative for AI. All susceptible birds are culled except for the 26 rare breads. Those have been tested and were negative and have been placed in quarantine. They will be tested regularly

## 26 Jan

## Bornebroek

NL-HPAI(P)-2026-00005

Broiler parent farm with around 70.000 chickens kept in one stable. An increase in the amount of death animals (300) was found. There are no poultry farms within a 1 km radius and 6 in a 3 km radius and 42 in the 10 km radius. Including a poultry slaughterhouse. A corridor has been established for this slaughterhouse.

