## Timeline HPAI outbreaks

## 29 Jan Wadenoijen

NL-HPAI(NON-P)-2026-00036

Trading farm in rare birds with 350 different kind of birds like ducks, swans, cranes, flamingos, parrots, coots, pigeons, etc. There has been in increase in dead and sick animals (flamingo, ibis, marabou). There are no other poultry farms in the 1 km and 3 km zone. In the 10 km zone there are 14 establishments with susceptible animals. No animals have been traded in the last period.

## 30 Jan Dalen NL-HPAI(P)-2026-00006

Laying hen farm with 14.600 hens. An increase in dead and sick animals. Pathological signs like petechiae in the heart and kidneys. In the 1 km zone no poultry farms in the 3 km 1 and in the 10 km zone 11

## 03 Feb Winterswijk NL-HPAI(NON-P)-2026-00037

Hobby farm with 12 geese, 11 of which were dead. No zoning due to limited amount of birds

## 07 Feb Kamerik NL-HPAI(NON-P)-2026-00056

Recreation park with 48 birds at the park (turkeys, pheasants, geese, and chickens). There has been an increase in mortality. No zoning due to limited amount of birds NL-HPAI(P)-2026-00007

## 07 Feb

## Moergestel

Turkey farm with around 35.600 animals divided across 5 stables. In one stable an increase in the number of dead animals was found. In  km zone no other farms. In the 3 km zone 4 poultry farms and in the 10 km zone 21 poultry farms

