## Timeline HPAI outbreaks

## 14 Feb Vlagtwedde

NL-HPAI(P)-2026-00008

Laying hen farm with around 34.000 animals distributed across 2 stables. In increase in dead animals and sick animals with severe clinical signs were found. No poultry farm in the 1 km zone and 1 in the 3 km zone and 15  in the 10 km zone.

## 18 Feb

## Aalsum

NL-HPAI(P)-2026-00009

Organic laying hen farm with two barns with around 30,000 laying hens. One section experienced an increased mortality (more than 70 per day), lethargy, red combs, a drop in production, and reduced feed intake. There are no other poultry farms within a 1 km radius. There are two other poultry farms within a 3 km radius. Within a 10 km radius, there are 11 additional locations with poultry, including a poultry farmer who slaughters wild game.

In all outbreaks, the measures according 2016/429 and 2020/68 have been taken.

